


=Business Campaigns=

This application lets you keep track of all your marketing campaigns.

[campanyas-listado.png]

==List of commercial campaigns.==

The list of commercial campaigns. you will find the most important pillars of registration:

- **Ref.:** Numeric code that identifies the marketing year.
- **Home:** Date of commencement of commercial campaign.
- **End:** Daylight commercial campaign.
- **Name:** Name of the marketing year.
- **State:** State in which is the marketing year. (Planned, Begun, Cancelled, Finished).
- **NPC:** Number of possible customers included in the marketing year.
- **NCL:** Number of clients including in marketing year.
- **NAG:** Number of events in the marketing year.
- **NPR:** Number of estimates made by the commercial campaign.
- **NPY:** Number of projects carried out by the commercial campaign.
- **NC:** Number of comments entered this campaign.
- **NF:** Number of files associated with this campaign.


**Remember**: The events can be arranged by dragging them to the user folder you want.

