==Form marketing campaigns==

This is the application of marketing campaigns, with it you can add, modify and view all data of different marketing campaigns carried out in the state, the information is classified in different tabs: main data, comments, file attachments, data on the registry modifications and assignments to folders.

===Data Tab campaign===

In this tab you can view and modify the main details about the campaign. Here we relate all information fields.

[campanyas-formulario.png]

- **Name (*):** Trade name of the marketing year.
- **State (*):** State in which is the marketing year.
- **Home (*):** Date of commencement of commercial campaign.
- **Fin (*):** Daylight commercial campaign.
- **Description:** Brief description of the marketing year.


(*) **Required when creating or modifying a campaign Campos.**

